metadata.description:
Space Whale 
2021 | 1/1 Edition
4168 x 4168 px | 150 dpi | .png

Background
The « Space Whale » is guarding the 9th world. But something is silently looming, watching through space and time. To be sure that the deepest secret of this world remain kept.

There is a saying that something is hidden inside this monochromatic illustration.

Enigma
« ...Human.
Defeat Entropy.
Chase them through space and time.
Solve the Enigma.
Only the alpha will receive the omega. »
